      <p style="margin-bottom:0;"><strong>PrimeKey Analysis</strong> is a proprietary 8-pillar scoring system that grades a Singapore property from 0–100% — an objective <em>Investability Score</em> built on connectivity, growth zones, land-sale catalysts, project size, tenure, yield, schools, and upgrader demand. It's designed to <strong>protect the downside</strong> first, so the upside can take care of itself. See a Green score, sign with confidence. See Yellow or Red, and you'll know to slow down — long before the OTP is in front of you.</p>
